    <introduction>
      <Value><![CDATA[<p>Queen Margaret University, Edinburgh is looking for food and drink lovers of all ages to take part in food tasting panels at its campus in Musselburgh. Attendance on the panel would suit people aged 18 years and upwards who can take part in occasional panels mainly during week days. Participants will be rewarded after each short tasting session with a £10 gift voucher.</p>]]></Value>
